n="0771c17" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0771c17"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000025190">洛京伏牛山</placeName><persName key="A010392">自在</persName>傳（<persName key="A010447">一鉢和尚</persName> <persName key="A005287">南印</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0771c18"/><persName key="A010392">釋自在</persName>俗姓李，<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName>人也，生有奇瑞。稍長，<lb
ed="T" n="0771c19"/>坐則加趺，親黨異之。辭所愛投<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName>出家，<lb
ed="T" n="0771c20"/>於<placeName key="PL000000012005">新定</placeName>登戒。及諸方參學，從<placeName key="PL000000019349">南康</placeName><persName key="A003623">道一禪<lb
ed="T" n="0771c21"/>師</persName>法席，懸解真宗，逸蹤流輩，道譽孔昭，行<lb
ed="T" n="0771c22"/><anchor xml:id="beg0771sgsz4"/>止<anchor xml:id="end0771sgsz4"/>優游。多隱山谷，四方禪侶叢萃其門。<date from-iso="0806" key="j20154742020606" to-iso="0820">元和<lb
ed="T" n="0771c23"/>中</date>，居<placeName key="PL000000023650">洛下香山</placeName>，與<persName key="A009460">天然禪師</persName>為莫逆之交。<lb
ed="T" n="0771c24"/>所遊必好古，思得前賢遺跡以快逸觀。<placeName key="PL000000023647">龍<lb
ed="T" n="0771c25"/>門山</placeName>得<persName key="A001357">後魏三藏</persName>翻經處；<placeName key="PL000000024601">王屋山</placeName>得<persName key="A004688">稠禪師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0771c26"/>解虎鬪處，此山飲甘泉，改為<placeName key="PL000000024605">甘泉寺</placeName>；<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0771c27"/>得<persName key="A010446">梵法師</persName>馬跑泉。居無戀著，所著《三傷歌》，<lb
ed="T" n="0771c28"/>辭理俱美，警發迷蒙，有益於代。<ref type="person" target="#A006589">前蜀王氏</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0771c29"/>偽<date from-iso="0919" key="j20567572057302" to-iso="0920">乾德初</date>，有小軍使陳公娶<persName key="A008497">高中令駢</persName>諸孫<pb ed="T" n="0772a" xml:id="T50.2061.0772a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0772a01"/>女，<ref type="person" target="#A008497">若人</ref>持不殺二十餘年，後在<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>為男婚<lb
ed="T" n="0772a02"/>娶，禮須屠宰。<persName key="A008497">高</persName>初不欲，親戚言：「自己持戒，<lb
ed="T" n="0772a03"/>行禮酒筵將何以娛賓也？」依違之際，遂多庖<lb
ed="T" n="0772a04"/>割。俄未浹旬，得疾頗異，口但慌言，已而三<lb
ed="T" n="0772a05"/>宿還<anchor xml:id="beg0772sgsz1"/>蘇<anchor xml:id="end0772sgsz1"/>，述冥間之事。初被黑衣使者追攝<lb
ed="T" n="0772a06"/>入<placeName key="PL000000042848"><anchor xml:id="beg0772sgsz2"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0772sgsz2"/>府</placeName>城隍廟，廟神峨冠大袖，與一金甲武<lb
ed="T" n="0772a07"/>士<anchor xml:id="beg0772sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>唔</sic><corr>晤</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0772sgsz3"/>坐。使者領<persName key="A008497">高</persName>見神，武士言語紛紜，讓<lb
ed="T" n="0772a08"/><persName key="A008497">高</persName>破戒，仍扼腕<anchor xml:id="beg0772sgsz4"/>罵<anchor xml:id="end0772sgsz4"/>曰：「吾護戒神將也。為<ref type="person" target="#A008497">汝</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0772a09"/>二十年食寢不遑，豈期忽起殺心，頓虧戒<lb
ed="T" n="0772a10"/>檢？命雖未盡，罪亦頗深，須送冥司懲其故<lb
ed="T" n="0772a11"/>犯。」城隍神問<persName key="A008497">高</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A008497">汝</ref>更修何善追贖過尤<lb
ed="T" n="0772a12"/>乎？」<persName key="A008497">高</persName>常誦持《上生經》，其數已多，于時懵然<lb
ed="T" n="0772a13"/>都無記憶，恐懼之間白曰：「誦得《三傷頌》、《一鉢<lb
ed="T" n="0772a14"/>和尚歌》。」遂合掌向神厲聲而念，神與武士<lb
ed="T" n="0772a15"/>聳耳擎拳立聽，顏色漸怡。及卒章，神皆涕<lb
ed="T" n="0772a16"/>淚，乃謂<persName key="A008497">高</persName>曰：「且歸人間，宜切營善。」拜辭未<lb
ed="T" n="0772a17"/>畢，颯然起坐，備陳厥事。自此《三傷》《一鉢》之歌<lb
ed="T" n="0772a18"/>頌，人皆傳寫諷誦焉。<persName key="A010447">一鉢和尚</persName>者歌詞叶理，<lb
ed="T" n="0772a19"/>激勸憂思之深，然文體涉里巷，豈加《三傷》<lb
ed="T" n="0772a20"/>之典雅乎？<persName key="A010392">在</persName>遣弟子去<placeName key="PL000000000197">江南</placeName>，選山水之最<lb
ed="T" n="0772a21"/>者，「<ref type="person" target="#A010392">吾</ref>願往中終老」。到<placeName key="PL000000018987">江州都昌縣</placeName>有好林<lb
ed="T" n="0772a22"/>泉，迴報。<persName key="A010392">在</persName>行至<placeName key="PL000000023951">葉縣</placeName>，道俗所留。往<placeName key="PL000000028294">隋州開<lb
ed="T" n="0772a23"/>元寺</placeName>示滅，年八十一，則<date from-iso="0821-02-13" key="j20209682021319" to-iso="0822-01-30">長慶元年</date>也。</p>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0772a24"/>系曰：稽諸律藏，出家者犯戒，則招二罪，一<lb
ed="T" n="0772a25"/>違制，二業道也。<persName key="A008497">高<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>在家素不受戒，無違<lb
ed="T" n="0772a26"/>制愆，俗容有業道罪，寧得有護戒神邪？<lb
ed="T" n="0772a27"/>況<persName key="A008497">高<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>既持不殺，則冥然感止持無作之善<lb
ed="T" n="0772a28"/>生焉。因鮮克有終，致遭幽責，告諸五眾，<lb
ed="T" n="0772a29"/><anchor xml:id="beg0772sgsz5"/>當<anchor xml:id="end0772sgsz5"/>畏護戒之神。夫如是，明則有戒法，幽則<pb ed="T" n="0772b" xml:id="T50.2061.0772b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0772b01"/>有鬼神歟！</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0772b0201"><lb
ed="T" n="0772b02"/>次<placeName key="PL000000034762">成都府元和聖壽寺</placeName><persName key="A005287">釋南印</persName>，姓張氏。明寤<lb
ed="T" n="0772b03"/>之性，受益無厭，得<ref type="person" target="#A001719">曹溪</ref>深旨，無以為證。<lb
ed="T" n="0772b04"/>見<placeName key="PL000000034714">淨眾寺</placeName><persName key="A010304">會師</persName>，所謂落機之錦，濯以增<anchor xml:id="beg0772sgsz6"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>研</sic><corr>妍</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0772sgsz6"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0772b05"/>銜燭之龍，行而破暗。<persName key="A005287">印</persName>自<placeName key="PL000000027764">江陵</placeName>入<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>，於<placeName key="PL000000034674">蜀<lb
ed="T" n="0772b06"/>江</placeName>之南壖，薙草結<anchor xml:id="beg0772sgsz7"/>茆<anchor xml:id="end0772sgsz7"/>，眾皆歸仰，漸成佛宇，<lb
ed="T" n="0772b07"/><date key="j20078242008178" from-iso="0785-02-18" to-iso="0786-02-07">貞元初年</date>也。<persName key="A004371">高司空崇文</persName>平<persName key="A009181">劉闢</persName>之後，改<lb
ed="T" n="0772b08"/>此寺為<placeName key="PL000000034762">元和聖壽</placeName>，初名<placeName key="PL000000034762">寶應</placeName>也。<persName key="A005287">印</persName>化緣將<lb
ed="T" n="0772b09"/>畢，於<date from-iso="0821" key="j20209682022078" to-iso="0824">長慶初</date>示疾入滅。營塔葬<anchor xml:id="beg0772001"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0772001"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000034762">寺</ref>中。<lb
ed="T" n="0772b10"/><date from-iso="0841" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="0846">會昌</date>中毀塔，<date from-iso="0847" key="j20304612035056" to-iso="0859">大中</date>復於<placeName key="PL000000034762">江北寶應</placeName>舊基上<lb
ed="T" n="0772b11"/>創此寺，還名「聖壽」。<persName key="A005287">印</persName>弟子傳嗣有<persName key="A010450">義俛</persName>，復<lb
ed="T" n="0772b12"/>興禪法焉。</p>
